Package: RSCUcaller
Type: Package
Title: Program in R for calculating RSCU.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Mateusz",
             family = "Mazdziarz",
             role = c("cre", "aut"),
             email = "mazdziarzm@gmail.com"))
Description: The RSCUcaller package offers a comprehensive toolkit for analyzing relative synonymous codon usage (RSCU) values across multiple DNA sequences. Specifically, this package allows users to retrieve RSCU information by efficiently extracting and organizing RSCU data from input DNA sequences, providing a structured format for further analysis. For visualizing RSCU values, the package offers plotting functions to generate graphical representations of RSCU values, enabling researchers to visually identify patterns and trends in codon usage. For calculating statistical significance, RSCUcaller includes statistical methods to determine the significance of observed codon usage biases, facilitating rigorous data interpretation.
